44\u0652\u0641\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0631\u0650","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"quran-simple","language":"ar","name":"Simple","englishName":"Simple","format":"text","type":"quran"}},{"number":97,"name":"\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u062f\u0631","englishName":"Al-Qadr","englishNameTranslation":"The Power, Fate","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":5,"ayahs":[{"text":"In the name of God, The Most Gracious, The Dispenser of Grace:"},{"number":6126,"text":"BEHOLD, from on high have We bestowed this [divine writ] on Night of Destiny.","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30},{"number":6127,"text":"And what could make thee conceive what it is, that Night of Destiny?","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30},{"number":6128,"text":"The Night of Destiny is better than a thousand months:","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30},{"number":6129,"text":"in hosts descend in it the angels, bearing divine inspiration by their Sustainer's leave; from all [evil] that may happen","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30},{"number":6130,"text":"does it make secure, until the rise of dawn.","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"en.asad","language":"en","name":"Asad","englishName":"Muhammad Asad","format":"text","type":"translation"}}]}